race.comment: THE HAIRDRESSER (1) has put back-to-back wins together and it's hard to knock mares in form. Gets Wiggins on top from the inside marble and is capable of bringing up the hat-trick against this lot. The lightly-raced OUR IMPACT (6) will be ready to peak now third-up from the spell and looks the runner in this field with the most upside. Should be right there when the judge calls a halt. LET'S RIDE (8) has hit the top-five in seven of her past eight starts and is usually thereabouts. Top-three credentials on best form. GOODNIGHT ROMEO (3) was well in the betting at the latest outing and where there's smoke there's fire. Keep very safe. SIR MAXIMUS (5) rounds out the selections.
